rComments: Professor Anderson gives great lectures, but they're very content heavy. He posts his slides (which are amazing), but they're incomplete so you must go to class for a good grade. He can seem a little unsure of himself regarding assignments, but is well-spoken and gives lectures confidently. Assignments are hit or miss. Would certainly take again.

he has the best lecture slides of any prof I've ever had, hands down! his exams are an easy 4.0. but the assignments are pretty difficult because he cant explain them properly and his expectations are very unclear. he is super helpful though, but the assignments can really get some people.
